{"tid":1531580,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"十月十日去邊慶祝國慶","createTime":"2019-09-02T09:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T10:05:48.000Z","uid":261705,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6b1afaaa9adc32e0aadd154b4ee3a98fd6a1565b","tid":1531580,"uid":261705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:17:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n慶祝文哥成功推翻獨裁政權<br />\n教育下一代學文哥為自由付出<br />\n可惜無知者未能忍耐政權交替嘅政治陣痛期<br />\n唔係努力幫手消除初期建設被逼拉攏嘅軍閥勢力<br />\n反易直接造反<br />\n將五勞七傷嘅中國推回戰亂"},{"pid":"8b7c4669644366eff1411c0874c438dacd449369","tid":1531580,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:17:50.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a6aa2a0369859ddfd57c1d1e7981322e8f59bf","tid":1531580,"uid":256632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:17:51.000Z","msg":"【持續更新】香港人九月日程表<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/kEaguAX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/kEaguAX</a>"},{"pid":"6f6943105bcbfe90222ee2d14a346f527b603ef9","tid":1531580,"uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:19:07.000Z","msg":"中國係屬於台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支持一個中國"},{"pid":"c5441b5d9e1c4b985d5db62c2fce5584d1179ce7","tid":1531580,"uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:19:55.000Z","msg":"台灣先係真正既中國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a58f45e7c26f3edcf4e6202c7b24d771eb4c5a4","tid":1531580,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:27:13.000Z","msg":"上世紀六十年代，七十年代，台灣好多雙十慶典旅行團，蔣公有補貼比香港同胞，條件係參加一天雙十國慶，跟著做乜都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5edfc976362ce0f3c4d6c2114ffd77773dd41f6c","tid":1531580,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:31:51.000Z","msg":"往年紅樓有升旗🇹🇼🇹🇼"},{"pid":"381f4c3384956d707dd60e99a91a5188623d4a1c","tid":1531580,"uid":98731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:32:16.000Z","msg":"【美國巴絲】請聯絡你嘅地區同州嘅國會代表／議員<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dNDHwS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dNDHwS</a>"},{"pid":"5bc94793d45904b23d330610fb0f192cd53b5fc1","tid":1531580,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:34:09.000Z","msg":"既然一個中國 當然十月十號都係一樣國家重要日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10973b31ac1ce595e61a1e39314d2379fde29c69","tid":1531580,"uid":288900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:44:20.000Z","msg":"加入慶祝雙十國慶，正統政權108年國慶!"},{"pid":"5b26afd2f8f2e8574748ce21dcf8caf7520075c1","tid":1531580,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10973b31ac1ce595e61a1e39314d2379fde29c69","tid":1531580,"uid":288900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:44:20.000Z","msg":"加入慶祝雙十國慶，正統政權108年國慶!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch